01:33:38,822 --> 01:33:39,923
His wheels?

1187
01:33:41,366 --> 01:33:42,968
And he's the perfect patient.

1188
01:33:43,118 --> 01:33:44,390
He's so funny!

1189
01:33:44,619 --> 01:33:45,770
When you read about him...

1190
01:33:45,870 --> 01:33:48,143
