- (LAUGHING)

1254
01:39:32,925 --> 01:39:34,151
I bet you did.

1255
01:39:34,760 --> 01:39:36,157
(LAUGHING)

1256
01:39:41,601 --> 01:39:44,580
Stephen, I need to steal you.
